config = model.get_config()
classifier = KerasGClassifier(config)
params = {'layers_3_Dense__config__kernel_initializer__config__scale': 2.0,
    'layers_2_Activation': None, 'lr': 0.05}
classifier.set_params(**params)
got1 = len(classifier.config['layers'])
got2 = classifier.lr
got3 = classifier.config['layers'][2]['config']['kernel_initializer']['config'
    ]['scale']
assert got1 == 3, got1
assert got2 == 0.05, got2
assert got3 == 2.0, got3
